title: CAKE EMISSIONS REDUCTION
body:
We’re proposing to reduce CAKE emissions allocated to the PancakeSwap farm.

The three options you can choose to vote on are:

❌ **No change:**
 **15 CAKE** go to yield farms
Total emissions =  **25 CAKE per block (including Syrup Pool)**

🔥 **10% reduction to farms:**
**13.5 CAKE** go to yield farms
New total emissions = **23.5 CAKE per block (including Syrup Pool)**

🔥🔥 **20% reduction to farms:**
**12 CAKE** go to yield farms
New total emissions = **22 CAKE per block (including Syrup Pool)
